		<li>
		<p style="text-align: justify">Revitalization of the DTI's Information System Integration Project (P73.3m) 
		</p>
		</li>
		<li>
		<p style="text-align: justify">Digital Philippines (P36m) </p>
		</li>
		<li>
		<p style="text-align: justify">Regional Competitiveness Program (P25m) 
		</p>
		</li>
		<li>
		<p style="text-align: justify">Industry 4.0: Preparing Philippine Industries for Future Production (P20m) 
		</p>
		</li>
		<li>
		<p style="text-align: justify">Bamboo Development Program (P10m) </p>
		</li>
		<li>
		<p style="text-align: justify">GoLokal! (P10m) </p>
		</li>
		<li>
		<p style="text-align: justify">Halal Accreditation (P7.3m) </p>
		</li>
